Corrinne Wicks https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Corrinne_Wicks 0 Corrinne Wicks (born 1968) is an English actress, notable for playing Dr. Helen Thompson in the BBC daytime soap opera Doctors, from 2000 to 2005, and Ella Hart in the ITV soap opera Emmerdale, from 2010 to 2011.
